'''華沙朗·江詩丹頓'''（英语：'''Vacheron Constantin'''，法語發音：​[va.ʃə.rɔ̃ kɔ̃s.tɑ̃.tɛ̃]），通稱'''江詩丹頓'''，是[[瑞士|瑞士]]名贵[[鐘錶|鐘錶]]品牌、生产商，于1755年创立，总部位于瑞士[[日內瓦州|日內瓦州]]的[[普朗莱瓦特|普朗莱瓦特]]。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XVIII|title=Birth of the Vacheron Constantin Manufacture of Haute Horlogerie - Vacheron Constantin|website=heritage.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217171542/http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XVIII|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/paidpost/vacheron/the-shape-of-harmony/260-years-of-excellence.html|title=260 Years of Excellence (Paid Post by vacheron from NYTimes.com)|date=2018-10-01|work=The New York Times|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602235939/https://www.nytimes.com/paidpost/vacheron/the-shape-of-harmony/260-years-of-excellence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 江诗丹顿是世界上最古老的钟表品牌之一，1996年起，隸屬於瑞士的[[历峰集团|历峰集团]]（Richemont Group），其钟表生产历史自创立起从未间断。<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":0" /><ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.richemont.com/10-press-news/other-group-announcements/142-juan-carlos-torres-to-succeed-claude-daniel-proellochs-as-chief-executive-of-vacheron-constantin.html|title=Compagnie Financière Richemont SA - Juan-Carlos Torres to succeed Claude-Daniel Proellochs as Chief Executive of Vacheron Constantin|website=www.richemont.com|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122092441/https://www.richemont.com/10-press-news/other-group-announcements/142-juan-carlos-torres-to-succeed-claude-daniel-proellochs-as-chief-executive-of-vacheron-constantin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该公司在全球范围内共拥有約1200名員工（2018年），大部份員工在日內瓦總部或汝拉山谷（Vallée de Joux）零件製造廠工作。<ref name=":29">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/18/fashion/watches-vacheron-constantin-juan-carlos-torres.html|title=Brand Awareness is the Goal at Vacheron Constantin|last=Gomelsky|first=Victoria|date=2016-11-16|work=The New York Times|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133640/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/18/fashion/watches-vacheron-constantin-juan-carlos-torres.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

江詩丹頓是世界上最著名的名贵钟表品牌之一。<ref name=":29" /><ref name=":9">{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/features/5-reasons-collectors-love-Vacheron-Constantin-8168-1.aspx|title=5 reasons collectors love Vacheron Constantin {{!}} Christie's|language=en|website=www.christies.com|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811005902/https://www.christies.com/features/5-reasons-collectors-love-Vacheron-Constantin-8168-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mrporter.com/journal/about-time/introducing-vacheron-constantin/3776|title=Introducing Vacheron Constantin|last=PORTER|first=MR|website=Introducing Vacheron Constantin {{!}} About Time {{!}} The Journal {{!}} Issue 387 {{!}} 05 September 2018 {{!}} MR PORTER|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602155123/https://www.mrporter.com/journal/about-time/introducing-vacheron-constantin/3776|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/s/vacheron-constantin/|title=Vacheron Constantin - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|accessdate=2019-01-18|work=www.hautehorlogerie.org|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128054422/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/s/vacheron-constantin/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://shop.hodinkee.com/blogs/journal/vacheron-constantin-historiques-collection-highlights|title=In The Shop: The Vacheron Constantin Historiques Collection|website=HODINKEE Shop|language=en|access-date=2019-02-03|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125013301/https://shop.hodinkee.com/blogs/journal/vacheron-constantin-historiques-collection-highlights|dead-url=no}}</ref> 多年来，江诗丹顿的客户及佩戴者中不乏显赫人士，包括英国女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]、[[教宗庇護十一世|教皇庇護十一世]]、法国皇帝[[拿破崙一世|拿破崙一世]]、[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡]]影帝[[马龙·白兰度|马龙·白兰度]]、美国心理学之父[[威廉·詹姆士|威廉·詹姆士]]、石油大王[[约翰·洛克菲勒|约翰·洛克菲勒]]、英国[[戴安娜王妃|戴安娜王妃]]、美国总统[[哈瑞·杜魯門|哈瑞·杜魯門]]、人类飞行先驱[[莱特兄弟|莱特兄弟]]等等。<ref name=":9" /><ref name=":22" /><ref name=":5" /><ref name=":30">{{Cite web|url=http://life.executive-magazine.com/design/jewelleryandwatches/worlds-oldest-watchmaker-opens-boutique-beirut|title=World's oldest watchmaker opens boutique in Beirut|date=2016-11-30|website=Executive Life|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-16|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617015309/https://life.executive-magazine.com/design/jewelleryandwatches/worlds-oldest-watchmaker-opens-boutique-beirut|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3" /> 而江诗丹顿为[[埃及|埃及]]国王[[福阿德一世|福阿德一世]]（Fuad I of Egypt）订制的[[怀表|怀表]]No. 402833 (1929) 是世界上拍卖成交价最高的怀表之一，于2005年4月3日由[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]以约277万美金在瑞士日内瓦售出（3,306,250[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]）。<ref name=":110">{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-79-182?browse_all=1&page=1&q=King+Fouad+Vacheron|title=King Fouad Vacheron & Constantin, Genève, No. 402833, case No. 251058.|last=|first=|date=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924082336/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-79-182?browse_all=1&page=1&q=King+Fouad+Vacheron|archive-date=2020-09-24|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-11-26}}</ref><ref name=":02">{{Cite news|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/most-expensive-watches-sold-at-auction-2013-5#19-in-november-2011-antiquorum-sold-a-full-24-hour-repeating-patek-philippe-pocket-watch-for-229-million-6|title=The 24 Most Expensive Watches Ever Sold At Auction|work=Business Insider|access-date=2018-11-26|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803122427/https://www.businessinsider.com/most-expensive-watches-sold-at-auction-2013-5#19-in-november-2011-antiquorum-sold-a-full-24-hour-repeating-patek-philippe-pocket-watch-for-229-million-6|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年，江诗丹顿制造出订制款的[[Reference_57260|Reference_57260]]怀表，该怀表保持世界最复杂机械表记录至今、拥有57项复杂功能。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-09-17/vacheron-constantin-unveils-the-most-complicated-watch-ever-made|title=Vacheron Constantin Unveils the Most Complicated Watch Ever Made|accessdate=2015-09-18|date=September 17, 2015|last=Pulvirent|first=Stephen|publisher=[[bloomberg.com|bloomberg.com]]|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224113/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-09-17/vacheron-constantin-unveils-the-most-complicated-watch-ever-made|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://monochrome-watches.com/vacheron-constantin-ref-57260-the-worlds-most-complicated-watch-with-57-complications/|title=Vacheron Constantin ref.57260 – the World’s Most Complicated Watch with 57 Complications|accessdate=2015-09-18|date=17 September 2015|last=|first=|publisher=monochrome-watches.com|website=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204143125/https://monochrome-watches.com/vacheron-constantin-ref-57260-the-worlds-most-complicated-watch-with-57-complications/|archive-date=2021-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==

=== 早期历史 ===
[[File:Francois_Constantin_Clockmaker.jpg|缩略图]]
公司創立於1755年，創辦人[[让-马克·瓦舍龙|让-马克·瓦舍龙]]（Jean-Marc Vacheron）是一位[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日內瓦|日內瓦]]的獨立製錶師。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cigaraficionado.com/article/father-time-swiss-watches-7430|title=Father Time: Swiss Watches|accessdate=2019-01-17|last=Inc|first=M. Shanken Communications|work=Cigar Aficionado|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126220101/https://www.cigaraficionado.com/article/father-time-swiss-watches-7430|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="lepointmontres">[http://montres.lepoint.fr/Magazine/Grand-horlogers/jean-marc-vacheron-03-12-2012-1539096_827.php Jean-Marc Vacheron: 1731 - 1805, Suisse], ''[[Le_Point|Le Point]]''</ref> 因对[[哲学|哲学]]、科学和制表学有着共同兴趣，瓦舍龙和法国[[启蒙运动|启蒙运动]]代表人物[[让-雅克·卢梭|卢梭]]、[[伏爾泰|伏尔泰]]均是好朋友。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/vacheron-constantin-ticks-over-250-years/4671654|title=Vacheron Constantin ticks over 250 years|last=swissinfo.ch|first=S. W. I.|last2=Corporation|first2=a branch of the Swiss Broadcasting|website=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=en|access-date=2019-02-26|archive-date=2019-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226173134/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/vacheron-constantin-ticks-over-250-years/4671654|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lkyspp.nus.edu.sg/docs/default-source/ips/sp_tk_treasures-of-vacheron-constantin_230611.pdf|title=Opening of "Treasures of Vacheron Constantin - A Legacy of Watchmaking since 1755" Exhinibition|last=|first=|date=|website=National University of Singapore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226173251/https://lkyspp.nus.edu.sg/docs/default-source/ips/sp_tk_treasures-of-vacheron-constantin_230611.pdf|archive-date=2019-02-26|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chronosplus.gr/en_US/nea/news-articles/h-vacheron-constantin-tima-ton-jean-jacques-rousseau/|title=Vacheron Constantin honors Jean-Jacques Rousseau|date=2012-10-04|website=Chronos Plus|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-26|archive-date=2019-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226235624/http://www.chronosplus.gr/en_US/nea/news-articles/h-vacheron-constantin-tima-ton-jean-jacques-rousseau/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1785年，让-马克·瓦舍龙之子亞伯拉罕·瓦舍龙（Abraham Vacheron）继承家族事業。<ref name="lepointmontres" /> 這段時期正值[[法国大革命|法國大革命]]（1789-1799年），公司安然過渡。1810年，[[让-马克·瓦舍龙|让-马克·瓦舍龙]]之孫亞科斯-巴特雷米·瓦舍龙（Jacques-Barthélemy Vacheron）接管家業，成為公司的掌舵人，他更是首次將業務擴展到[[法國|法國]]和[[義大利|義大利]]。<ref name=":25">{{Cite web|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/vacheron-constantin/|work=www.hautehorlogerie.org|accessdate=2019-02-23|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127035654/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/vacheron-constantin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

其後，亞科斯發現孤身一人難以兼顧穿梭海外進行產品營銷，必須覓得一位合作夥伴處理公司業務，因此在1819年，弗朗索瓦·江詩丹頓（François Constantin）成為了他的合作伙伴，公司正式改名為“Vacheron & Constantin（中译：瓦舍龙和江诗丹顿）”。<ref name=":25" />弗朗索瓦·江詩丹頓將公司的鐘錶帶到世界各地，並開拓新市場，當中[[北美|北美]]為主要銷售區域。品牌一直沿用至今的座右銘「悉力以赴，精益求精（法语：Faire mieux si possible, ce qui est toujours possible）」首見於弗朗索瓦·江詩丹頓在1819年7月5日寫給亞科斯-巴特雷米·瓦舍龙的往來書信當中。<ref name=":25" />

1833年，喬治斯-奧古斯特·列修特（Georges-Auguste Leschot）受僱於江詩丹頓，負責監控生產程序。列修特是一位發明家，他革新的創作不僅成就了公司的成功，亦深遠地影響了整個製錶業的發展。他是首個成功規範化製錶業生產的人，並率先將机芯和其零件进行标准化制作。1844年，日內瓦藝術協會（Arts Society）將「裏維獎」（Rive Prize）金牌授予任职于江诗丹顿的喬治斯-奧古斯特·列修特，嘉奖他所发明的比例绘图仪（Pantograph）为“日内瓦工业最具价值的发现”。比例绘图仪可以确定机芯底盘和夹板中心位置并钻孔，这使得可更换零部件的生产成为可能，并提升了江诗丹顿腕表的品质。

=== 公司重组 ===
弗朗索瓦·江诗丹顿和亞科斯-巴特雷米·瓦舍龙分别于1854年和1863年去世，之后公司交由两家族的后代经营打理。1862年，江詩丹頓成為非导磁材料研究協會會員之一。

1877年，江诗丹顿创作了首枚非导磁时计，以完整杠杆机构抵御磁场影响。此机构包括平衡齿轮、平衡游丝和杠杆轴，均采用钯金属制造，配合以青铜打造的杠杆吊臂和金质擒纵轮。1880年，江诗丹顿開始以[[馬耳他十字|馬耳他十字]]作為其商標，並一直沿用至今。馬耳他十字原為機芯內的發條盒蓋上方的小零件，它的作用是防止發條匣被過度上錬，從而使時計運作更加準確。[[File:Vacheron-Constantin.JPG|缩略图]]

1887年，江诗丹顿在瑞士国家展览会上获得金牌，为公司奠下另一个里程碑。1906年，江诗丹顿于日内瓦开设首间专卖店，此店现址在Quai de l'Ile。

經濟大蕭條期間，百業艱難，江詩丹頓依然堅守本業。1936年，查理斯·江詩丹頓（Charles Constantin）掌管公司業務，成為自1850年代後首位來自江詩丹頓家族的掌舵人。1940年，Georges Ketterer 从查理斯·江詩丹頓手中收购江詩丹頓大部分股份。<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.europeanwatch.com/history/vacheron/|title=EWC: History of Vacheron Constantin|website=www.europeanwatch.com|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130073138/https://www.europeanwatch.com/history/vacheron/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 近期发展 ===
1969年，Georges Ketterer去世，公司交由其子Jacques Ketterer打理，并正式将“Vacheron & Constantin”更名为“Vacheron Constantin，（中文品牌名：江诗丹顿）”。<ref name=":4" />

1970年代，江诗丹顿受到[[石英危机|石英危机]]（quartz crisis）的冲击。1987年，[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]前石油部長及鐘錶收藏家沙克·阿美·扎奇·亞馬尼（Sheik Ahmed Zaki Yamani）成為品牌大股東後將瓦舍龙·江詩丹頓收納為其個人的持股組合。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/business/1987/11/29/yamani-is-handed-a-defeat-in-bid-for-swiss-watch-firm/f4408cdf-c5e4-4488-9494-9341419e5219/|title=YAMANI IS HANDED A DEFEAT IN BID FOR SWISS WATCH FIRM|work=Washington Post|language=en-US|issn=0190-8286|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608140353/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/business/1987/11/29/yamani-is-handed-a-defeat-in-bid-for-swiss-watch-firm/f4408cdf-c5e4-4488-9494-9341419e5219/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1996年，該部份的股份被瑞士的[[历峰集团|历峰集团]]（Richemont Group）全數收購。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=584e7cd0-fd06-11e8-9d6f-a36d95a3c5fa&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAxOC0wNy0xNi9ob3ctcmljaGVtb250LXBsYW5zLXRvLXN1cnZpdmUtaW4tYS1jaGFuZ2luZy0yMXN0LWNlbnR1cnktbWFya2V0cGxhY2U=|title=How Richemont Plans to Survive in a Changing 21st Century Marketplace|date=|last=|first=|website=www.bloomberg.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603113404/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=584e7cd0-fd06-11e8-9d6f-a36d95a3c5fa&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAxOC0wNy0xNi9ob3ctcmljaGVtb250LXBsYW5zLXRvLXN1cnZpdmUtaW4tYS1jaGFuZ2luZy0yMXN0LWNlbnR1cnktbWFya2V0cGxhY2U=|archive-date=2019-06-03|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-11}}</ref>

2004年，江詩丹頓于瑞士[[日內瓦州|日內瓦州]]的[[普朗莱瓦特|普朗莱瓦特市]]開設其全新總部及製錶廠。2005年10月，胡安·卡洛斯·托里斯（Juan Carlos Torres）被歷峰集團任命為江詩丹頓的全球首席执行官。江诗丹顿现为{{link-en|瑞士鐘錶行業聯合會|Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry}}（Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry）的主要成員，腕表年产量约为2万枚。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=V|title=Watch brands|date=|last=|first=|website=Federation of the swiss watch industry|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127075814/https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=V|archive-date=2021-01-27|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://chronohunter.com/brands/vacheron-constantin|title=Vacheron Constantin|language=en|website=chronohunter.com|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204105344/https://chronohunter.com/brands/vacheron-constantin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Vacheron Constantin and ‘The Human Touch’|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/20/fashion/watches-vacheron-constantin.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2019-03-20|accessdate=2019-03-21|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Robin|last=Swithinbank|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209130953/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/20/fashion/watches-vacheron-constantin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 公司口号 ==
江诗丹顿的一个公司口号是“悉力以赴，精益求精（Faire mieux si possible, ce qui est toujours possible）”。<ref name=":25" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=悉力以赴，精益求精|url=http://www.vacheron-constantin.cn/cn/manufacture/maison.html|work=Vacheron Constantin|accessdate=2019-01-23|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031212717/https://www.vacheron-constantin.cn/cn/manufacture/maison.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/paidpost/vacheron/the-shape-of-harmony/260-years-of-excellence.html|title=260 Years of Excellence (Paid Post by vacheron from NYTimes.com)|date=2018-10-01|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-01-23|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602235939/https://www.nytimes.com/paidpost/vacheron/the-shape-of-harmony/260-years-of-excellence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该口号最早出现在一封弗朗索瓦·江詩丹頓给亞科斯-巴特雷米·瓦舍龙的信中，该信件的日期1819年7月5号。<ref name=":33">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/vacheron-constantin/|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127035654/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/vacheron-constantin/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":253">{{Cite web|url=http://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/manufacture/maison.html|title=Do better if possible, and that is always possible|website=Vacheron Constantin|language=en|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120222410/https://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/manufacture/maison.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 钟表制造 ==
[[File:Watch_MET_66581.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Watch_MET_66581.jpg]]收藏的一枚江诗丹顿怀表]]

=== 重要发明及专利 ===
以下是江诗丹顿在钟表制造领域取得的部分成就。

* 1790年，创造出世界上第一项钟表的复杂功能<ref name=":24">{{Cite web|url=http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XVIII|title=Birth of the Vacheron Constantin Manufacture of Haute Horlogerie - Vacheron Constantin|website=heritage.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217171542/http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XVIII|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 1824年，发明了钟表的跳时显示功能（jumping hour）<ref name=":24" />
* 1885年，创造出第一款抗磁功能的时计
* 1901年，获得第一枚日内瓦印记（Geneval Seal）<ref name=":24" />
* 1929年，为[[埃及|埃及]]国王[[福阿德一世|福阿德一世]]（Fuad I of Egypt）订制的“很复杂”（Grande Complication）[[怀表|怀表]]No. 402833
* 1955年，创造出世界上最薄手动上链机芯（Calibre 1003）<ref name=":24" />
* 1992年，制造出世界上最薄的[[語音報時|三问报时]]表（Calibre 1755）<ref name=":24" />
* 2015年，制造出世界上最复杂的机械表（Reference 57260），拥有57项复杂功能<ref name=":15">{{Cite web|url=http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/the-worlds-most-complicated-watch|title=Vacheron Constantin reference 57260 - the most complicated watch|website=reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2018-11-30|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227125623/http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/the-worlds-most-complicated-watch|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite news|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/live-photos-of-vacheron-57260|title=Hands-On: The Vacheron Constantin 57260, The Most Complicated Watch In The World (Exclusive Live Photos, Thoughts) - HODINKEE|work=HODINKEE|language=en|access-date=2018-11-30|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118015055/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/live-photos-of-vacheron-57260|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 环保评级 ===
2018年12月，[[世界自然基金会|世界自然基金会]]（WWF）发布官方报告，包含对瑞士15个主要钟表及珠宝生产商的环保评级。<ref name=":44">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|title=Environmental rating and industry report 2018|last=|first=|date=|website=World Wide Fund for Nature|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103203525/https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF|archive-date=2020-11-03|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-19}}</ref><ref name=":45">{{Cite web|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|title=Swiss luxury watches fail to meet environmental standards|last=swissinfo.ch|first=S. W. I.|last2=Corporation|first2=a branch of the Swiss Broadcasting|website=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=en|access-date=2019-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129214749/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中江诗丹顿连同其它3个生产商（包括[[積家|积家]]、[[卡地亞|卡地亚]]）的评级为中上级（"Upper Midfield"），意味着作为钟表生产商江诗丹顿采取了一定的措施以消除其生产活动对环境及气候变化所造成的影响。<ref name=":44" />

在钟表及珠宝制造行业，主要的环保隐患有二：1）生产活动的不透明；2）对珍贵原材料的大量开采，主要包括[[金|金矿]]。而后者是造成众多环境问题的重要因素之一，比如水土污染、土壤退化、森林破坏等。<ref name=":44" /><ref name=":45" /> 在作为黄金最大生产国的发展中国家，包括中国、俄罗斯和南非，情况尤其严重。据估计，钟表及珠宝行业每年消耗超过2000吨的黄金，占全球黄金产量的50%以上，而大多数情况下，钟表制造公司不能或不愿意说明其原材料的来源,或原材料供应商是否采用环保的开采方式。<ref name=":44" />

== 著名表款 ==

=== 价格记录 ===
[[File:Watch_MET_66022.jpg|缩略图]]收藏的一枚江诗丹顿怀表]]

* 1979年，瓦舍龙·江詩丹頓推出「卡里斯泰」（Kallista），被視為歷史上最昂貴腕錶之一，原價值為五百萬美元，現今已升值至約一千一百萬美元。卡里斯泰鑲嵌了118顆祖母綠切割鑽石，結合製錶大師逾6,000小時工序和珠寶鑲嵌大師投放近20個月的心血製成。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://moneyinc.com/vacheron-watches/|title=10 of the Finest Vacheron Watches of All-Time|accessdate=10 July 2018|date=20 June 2016|publisher=|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120044113/https://moneyinc.com/vacheron-watches/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*2005年4月3日，江诗丹顿1929年为[[埃及|埃及]]国王[[福阿德一世|福阿德一世]]（Fuad I of Egypt）所订制的[[怀表|怀表]]No. 402833 (1929) 由[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]（Antiquorum）以约277万美金（3,306,250[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]）在日内瓦拍卖售出，成为世界表类拍卖成交价最高的怀表之一。<ref name=":110" /><ref name=":02" />
*2005年4月3日, 一枚江诗丹顿的神秘钟（mysterious clock）由安帝古伦拍卖行以约183万美金 (2,206,250瑞士法郎) 在日内瓦拍卖售出。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/users/sign_in|title=As a mysterious clock, L'sEsprit des Cabinotiers' sums up all that the Manufacture has offered over a quar-ter of a millennium, and indeed continues to offer at the most demanding and most accomplished level of haute horlogerie and artistic craftsmanship|last=|first=|date=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127162516/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/users/sign_in|archive-date=2021-01-27|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-02-18}}</ref>
* 2005年4月3日，江诗丹顿怀表「小島之旅」（Tour de I'lle）由安帝古伦拍卖行以约156万美金（1,876,250瑞士法郎）在日内瓦拍卖售出。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/auctions/79/top_lots|title=Tour de I'lle Antiquorum Vacheron Constantin|date=|last=|first=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924090318/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/auctions/79/top_lots|archive-date=2020-09-24|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=http://archive.org/details/ImportantModernVintageTimepieces-April2012|title=Important Modern & Vintage Timepieces - April 2012|last=www.ourivesariaportuguesa.info}}</ref>
* 2011年6月15日，江诗丹顿为美国汽车富商詹姆斯·柏加德（James W. Packard）订制的[[语音报时|三问]]怀表在纽约[[佳士得|佳士得]]拍卖行售出，最终成交价为176万美金。 <ref name=":31">{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/LotFinder/lot_details.aspx?intObjectID=5454553|title=VACHERON CONSTANTIN (MOVEMENT NO, 375551, CASE NO. 231922, MADE FOR JAMES WARD PACKARD IN 1918)|date=|last=|first=|language=en|website=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125141304/https://www.christies.com/LotFinder/lot_details.aspx?intObjectID=5454553|archive-date=2020-11-25|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-02}}</ref>

=== Overseas纵横四海系列腕表 ===
1996年，江詩丹頓開創其全新運動系列腕表，名為「纵横四海」（Overseas）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/featured/vintage-eye-for-the-modern-guy-vacheron-constantin-overseas/|title=Vintage Eye for the Modern Guy: Vacheron Constantin Overseas|accessdate=2018-12-21|date=2017-03-12|last=byCaleb|first=Written|work=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124040246/https://www.watchtime.com/featured/vintage-eye-for-the-modern-guy-vacheron-constantin-overseas/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而纵横四海系列腕表的前身 Ref. 222 腕表早在1977年[[石英危机|石英危机]]（quartz crisis）期间就已推出，该表款的设计师是Jorg Hysek。<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|url=http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XX|title=Technical and aesthetic daring, the specialty of Vacheron Constantin. - Vacheron Constantin|website=heritage.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2020-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209214906/http://heritage.vacheron-constantin.com/en/heritage/XX|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-vacheron-constantin-overseas-chronograph-now-with-the-geneva-hallmark-and-in-house-caliber-5200|title=Hands-On: The Vacheron Constantin Overseas Chronograph, Now With The Geneva Hallmark And In-House Caliber 5200|last=February 17|first=Arthur Touchot|language=en|last2=2016|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118003829/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/the-vacheron-constantin-overseas-chronograph-now-with-the-geneva-hallmark-and-in-house-caliber-5200|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://monochrome-watches.com/history-vacheron-constantin-overseas-1970s-icon/|title=The History of the Vacheron Constantin Overseas – The Other 1970s Icon|date=2016-11-01|language=en-US|website=Monochrome Watches|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130205557/https://monochrome-watches.com/history-vacheron-constantin-overseas-1970s-icon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2004年，原纵横四海系列表款经重新设计推出，并于2016年历经新一轮改款。<ref name=":12">{{Cite web|url=http://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/watches/overseas.html|title=Overseas|language=en|website=Vacheron Constantin|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118173026/https://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/watches/overseas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 部分纵横四海系列腕表具备复杂功能，包括计时表，世界时间，陀飞轮，月相，等等。<ref name=":11" /><ref name=":12" />

=== Patrimony传承系列腕表 ===
[[File:Vacheron_Constantin_Patrimony_gold_watch.jpg|缩略图]]Patrimony 传承系列腕表是江诗丹顿的旗舰表款之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/arieladams/2012/10/03/patrimony-answers-all-your-questions-about-swiss-watch-making/|title="Patrimony" Answers All Your Questions About Swiss Watch Making|last=Adams|first=Ariel|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126065930/https://www.forbes.com/sites/arieladams/2012/10/03/patrimony-answers-all-your-questions-about-swiss-watch-making/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":20">{{Cite web|url=https://www.truefacet.com/guide/closer-look-three-flagship-models-ultra-luxury-watchmakers/|title=3 Flagship Models from Ultra-Luxury Watchmakers {{!}} The Loupe, TrueFacet|date=2017-01-13|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116150015/https://www.truefacet.com/guide/closer-look-three-flagship-models-ultra-luxury-watchmakers/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该系列于2004年推出，以简洁高雅的设计风格和超薄表壳而著称。<ref name=":242">{{Cite web|url=https://www.europeanwatch.com/history/vacheron/|title=EWC: History of Vacheron Constantin|website=www.europeanwatch.com|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130073138/https://www.europeanwatch.com/history/vacheron/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该设计受到了江诗丹顿1950年代的部分表款启发。<ref name=":20" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en/watches/patrimony.html|title=Patrimony|language=en|website=Vacheron Constantin|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410062631/https://www.vacheron-constantin.com/en/watches/patrimony.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年，江诗丹顿决定将[[語音報時|三问报时]]复杂功能和部分Patrimony 腕表结合，而最终的产品就是世界上最薄的三问腕表——Patrimony Calibre 1731。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/featured/a-watch-of-note-the-inside-story-of-the-vacheron-constantin-patrimony-contemporaine-calibre-1731/|title=A Watch of Note: The Inside Story of the Vacheron Constantin Patrimony Contemporaine Calibre 1731|date=2015-03-28|last=byWatchTime|first=Written|language=en-US|website=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124040450/https://www.watchtime.com/featured/a-watch-of-note-the-inside-story-of-the-vacheron-constantin-patrimony-contemporaine-calibre-1731/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 现今的Patrimony 系列还包括一些其它复杂表款，比如[[萬年曆錶|万年历]]、[[月相|月相]]显示，等等。<ref name=":20" /><ref name=":242" />

=== Métiers d'Art艺术大师系列腕表 ===
2007年，江詩丹頓開創「艺术大师 - 面具」（Métiers d'Art Les Masques）系列，以微型藝術製作縮小版面具。品牌特意從日內瓦{{link-en|巴比爾穆勒前哥倫布博物館|Museu Barbier-Mueller d'Art Precolombí}}（法语：Museu Barbier-Mueller d'Art Precolombí）收藏中選取12款面具造型，在腕表表盘上打造微缩版本的面具雕塑，將部落藝術、腕錶製造藝術及精雕藝術三者合而為一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://watches.infoniac.com/index.php?page=post&id=3|title=Vacheron Constantin Metiers d'Art 'Les Masques'|access-date=2017-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010212753/http://watches.infoniac.com/index.php?page=post&id=3|archive-date=2016-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2012年，江詩丹頓開創「艺术大师 - 无限宇宙」（Métiers d'Art Les Univers Infinis）系列，以「平面密鑲鑲嵌法」的繪製理念在錶盤呈現多樣重複圖案，向荷蘭畫家[[莫里茲·柯尼利斯·艾雪|莫里茲·柯尼利斯·艾雪]]（Maurits Cornelis Escher）致敬。

=== 250周年纪念款 ===
2005年，適逢江詩丹頓250周年誌慶，公司推出「小島之旅」（Tour de I'lle）腕表。<ref name=":28">{{Cite web|url=https://www.totalprestigemagazine.com/vacheron-constantin-tour-de-ille/|title=Vacheron Constantin Tour De I’lle|date=2017-10-27|website=Totalprestige Magazine|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114163637/https://www.totalprestigemagazine.com/vacheron-constantin-tour-de-ille/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此時計拥有双面表盘、834件零件、擁有16項複雜功能，包括[[陀飞轮|陀飞轮]]、[[语音报时|三问报时]]、月相等等，其研发过程超过1万个小时。<ref name=":28" /><ref name=":26">{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-79-249|title=Tour de I'lle Antiquorum Vacheron Constantin|last=|first=|date=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116151756/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-79-249|archive-date=2021-01-16|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-04}}</ref>

“小岛之旅”腕表是世界上最复杂的腕表之一 。<ref name=":26" /> 江诗丹顿一共生产了7枚该腕表，每枚的售价超过1百万美金。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.millionairematch.com/top-3-luxuries/top-luxury-watches-vacheron-constantin-tour-de-i-lle--42-141|title=Top Luxury Watches: Vacheron Constantin Tour de I'lle|website=www.millionairematch.com|access-date=2019-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118201147/https://www.millionairematch.com/top-3-luxuries/top-luxury-watches-vacheron-constantin-tour-de-i-lle--42-141|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2005年4月3日，一枚“小岛之旅”腕表在瑞士日内瓦由[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]（Antiquorum）拍卖售出，最终成交价约156万美金 (1,876,250 瑞士法郎) 。<ref name=":26" /><ref name=":27">{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/ImportantModernVintageTimepieces-April2012|title=Important Modern & Vintage Timepieces - April 2012|last=www.ourivesariaportuguesa.info}}</ref> 拍卖售出的表款拥有独一无二的黑色表盘。<ref name=":26" />[[File:Fondation_de_la_Haute_Horlogerie_(Kremlin_exhibition)_by_shakko_22.jpg|缩略图]]

=== 260周年纪念款 ===
2015年，藉著品牌260周年，瓦舍龙·江詩丹頓推出製錶史上最精巧複雜的新款「Ref. 57260」怀表，這款時計由品牌的三位製錶師花費八年時間共同製作完成，共配備57項複雜功能，符合一位顧客的特別訂製要求。江詩丹頓不願透露的這款手錶的具體價格，但確認介於800萬美元至2,000萬美元之間。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2015-10-30/the-most-complicated-watch-ever-made|title=The Most Complicated Watch Ever Made|publisher=|via=www.bloomberg.com|access-date=2017-06-10|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609040455/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2015-10-30/the-most-complicated-watch-ever-made|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，三位研發Ref. 57260的江詩丹頓製錶師更榮獲日內瓦高級鐘錶大賞（The Grand Prix d'Horlogerie de Geneve）大獎。

江诗丹顿Ref.57260怀表是江诗丹顿订制款的超复杂系列怀表之一，最早的一款是由美国汽车富商詹姆斯·柏加德（James W. Packard）订制的[[语音报时|三问]]怀表，该怀表在纽约[[佳士得|佳士得]]拍卖行售出、最终成交价为176万美金。 <ref name=":31" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/tailor-made-complicated-watches|title=Vacheron Constantin reference 57260 - the most complicated watch|website=reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2019-04-01|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627024406/http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/tailor-made-complicated-watches|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此外，江诗丹顿1929年为[[埃及|埃及]]国王[[福阿德一世|福阿德一氏]]订制的No. 402833 (1929) 怀表是世界表类拍卖成交价最高的怀表之一，于2005年4月3日由[[安帝古倫拍賣行|安帝古伦拍卖行]]以约277万美金售出（3,306,250[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]）。<ref name=":110" /><ref name=":02" /> 1946年，江诗丹顿又为福阿德一氏的继任者[[法鲁克一世|法鲁克一世]]订制了一枚超复杂怀表，1948年也为法国的Guy de Boisrouvray[[伯爵|伯爵]]订制过一款超复杂怀表。<ref name="#2">{{Cite web|url=http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/king-farouk-egypt-watch|title=Vacheron Constantin reference 57260 - the most complicated watch|website=reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2018-11-30|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808012449/http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/king-farouk-egypt-watch|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/guy-de-boisrouvray-watch|title=Vacheron Constantin reference 57260 - the most complicated watch|website=reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com|access-date=2019-04-01|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808012439/http://reference57260.vacheron-constantin.com/en2/guy-de-boisrouvray-watch|dead-url=no}}</ref>

