*[[唐纳德·约翰·特朗普|唐纳德·约翰·特朗普]]，第45任美国总统（历史名作1968粉红金超薄腕表）
*[[埃德加·富尔|埃德加·富尔]]，[[法国|法国]]前总理（1955年日内瓦会议礼物手表）<ref name=":6" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-95-384?browse_all=1&page=7&q=vacheron+constantin|title=Vacheron & Constantin, Geneve, No. 513268, case No. 343124, Ref. 6032, made in 1955.|date=|last=|first=|website=catalog.antiquorum.swiss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924085349/https://catalog.antiquorum.swiss/en/lots/vacheron-constantin-lot-95-384?browse_all=1&page=7&q=vacheron+constantin|archive-date=2020-09-24|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-13}}</ref>
